title: MOTD.Live.Eng.v.USA.2008.05.28.WS.PDTV.XviD.
description:
Gary Lineker and guests (Lee Dixon, Alan Hansen and Alan Shearer) present live coverage of England v USA at Wembley. Fabio Capello will be hoping his side fare better than in their last match, which they lost 1-0 to France. While the rest of Europe\&#039;s major footballing nations prepare for this summer\&#039;s European Championships, England must instead turn their focus to the 2010 World Cup qualifiers, which begin in the autumn - and this friendly will give Capello another chance to work out his best XI. Includes the \&#039;Goal of the season\&#039; competition!

In addition to the MOTD Live coverage, post match interviews from BBC Interactive are also included. Ray Stubbs interviews John Terry, Fabio Capello, David Beckham and Mark Lawrenson.
